Aisha Yesufu, a popular Nigerian activist and co-convener has predicted that after Boko Haram Insurgents are done terrorizing the North, they would face the south. The activist said this in a Twitter post. She said; ”When Boko haram are done with the North they will face the South. If you think this is none of your business, some thought it wasn’t their business when it was happening in North East now it is.” Her comments are coming in the light of the attack on Government Science Secondary School, Kankara, Katsina State which the notorious terrorist group Boko Haram has claimed responsibility. Source Aisha Yesufu, the co-convener of the Bring Back Our Girls campaign has warned that Boko Haram terrorists will face the South when they are done with the North. She gave the warning to those who are showing 'I don't care attitude' to the worsening security situation in the north. She… December 16, 2020 In "News" The Governor of Kaduna state, Nasir El-Rufai has been dragged on Twitter and called names by Aisha Yesufu. The Bring Back Our Girls co-convener and #EndSARS protest frontliner, Aisha Yesufu called out El-Rufai over the state of insecurity in Kaduna state. Reacting to a tweet in which a lady notified… November 3, 2020 In "News" Aisha Yesufu, the co-convener of the BringBackOurGirls, BBOG, advocacy group has launched a fresh attack on President Muhammadu Buhari. Yesufu asked Buhari to vacate office because he has performed below expectation. She said the president has failed to ensure security of the North and the country. In a series of… March 2, 2018 In "Top Stories"